      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://betterthangrep.com&#34;&gt;Better than grep!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On Ubuntu, you need to install the package &lt;code&gt;ack-grep&lt;/code&gt; (oddly, the executable is also named ack-grep&amp;hellip;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Examples: find the usages of the variable &lt;code&gt;$secret&lt;/code&gt; in the PHP files&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;$ ack-grep --php &#39;\$secret&#39;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
